text: Orsières is a municipality of the district of Entremont in the canton of Valais in Switzerland. ==Villages== Branche, Chamoille, Champex-Lac, Chez-les- Addy-Maligue, Chez-les-Giroud, Chez-les-Reuses, Commeire, Issert, La Douay, La Fouly, La Rosière, Le Biolley, Les Archales, Orsières, Prassurny, Prayon, Praz-de-Fort, Reppaz, Somplaroz, Soulalex and Verlonnaz. ==References== ==Other websites== * Official website * Category:Cities in Switzerland Category:Municipalities in Entremont
